New Records: Botswana secured their first win in 6 matches with a 2-0 victory over Cape Verde
Key Match Events: Thabang Sesinyi scored Botswana's first goal in the 52nd minute
Omaatla Kebatho and Kabelo Seakanyeng received yellow cards for Botswana
Cape Verde had 14 shot attempts compared to Botswana's 7
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was played at Francistown Stadium in front of 8,000 fans
Referee Jessie Nkounkou Mvoutou oversaw the game
Others: Match was played on October 15, 2024, at 4:00 PM
